{"tid":2307114,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"53歲美女阿嬤「像20歲少女」！　比27年前年輕…47萬人看傻","createTime":"2020-12-01T03:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T16:32:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d547b8bbcd8c802806b7af1c39bdc181cded08d","tid":2307114,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"一般人對於阿嬤、媽媽的印象大多停留在「臉上看得出歲月痕跡」的想法，但印尼雅加達一位美女Puspa Dewi完全看不出來已經53歲，除了已經是媽媽，還抱了孫子當了阿嬤，因為外表保持得太好，和兒子勾手上街時還被誤認是情侶，顏值逆天讓人不敢相信。<br />\n<br />\nPuspa Dewi現年53歲，生下2個兒子，24歲的大兒子不久前才和妻子生下兒子，讓她當了阿嬤，而她的外表宛如20歲年輕正妹，臉上絲毫沒有皺紋外，身材也保持得相當魔鬼，她透露，自己熱愛運動，能有這樣凍齡的美貌，全是靠運動維持，平常也常在IG上分享私下的運動美照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5305/d5305476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5305%2Fd5305476.jpg&h=c7e95afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5305/d5305474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5305%2Fd5305474.jpg&h=85cc5d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為長得太美，Puspa Dewi和兒子勾著手出門時，常常會被路人誤以為是情侶，如果又抱著孫子，甚至還會被誤以為是兒子，她的老公哭笑不得，而她日前也PO出1993年和老公的合照，和現在一對比，現在竟然長得比27年前還要年輕，讓人驚訝不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5305/d5305475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5305%2Fd5305475.jpg&h=49665d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5305/d5305472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5305%2Fd5305472.jpg&h=43a35401&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"262976e42bb97401cd152a46014480bf99194c2d","tid":2307114,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"嘩痴咗孖筋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"